{"tid":112133,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"尋晚去Apple Store俾班仆街趕返出嚟","createTime":"2017-02-08T02:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T02:40:08.000Z","uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f6c661dd6be0dad64c1c7cd9d731aaa331713721","tid":112133,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T02:28:49.000Z","msg":"話說尋晚諗住去買MacBook，<br />\n就收工特登去尖沙咀間Apple store到睇啦，<br />\n點知睇睇吓突然放咗個勁臭嘅屁，<br />\n臭到連大半間store嘅人都聞到，<br />\n我即刻面仔都紅埋覺得唔好意思<br />\n本來諗住扮無事繼續睇嘢，<br />\n突然班staff就走埋嚟話請我出去，<br />\n我心諗你地無撚嘢吓話？放屁咋喎，<br />\n嗰陣搞到我勁老尷，成間store啲人都望晒過嚟，<br />\n我就邊走邊屌：<br />\n「屌你咁撚大間store都唔整返個窗，好打有限啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實嚟想問吓大家而家邊到買mbpr最抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3074e2b606a43ad2c153e8506d87be51b4a373","tid":112133,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T02:30:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd15d4a9ff80b4bcc9ef271772ce51216fb7f50","tid":112133,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T02:35:15.000Z","msg":"0分，唔好笑唔通順，冇起承轉合"},{"pid":"f086fe48f5d26f17b98ae4f6096f4ab8b179beb2","tid":112133,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T02:40:08.000Z","msg":"你個屎眼可以撐馬桶咁大嫁<br />\n放次屁可以半間apple store 都聞到"}]}